                </p>
                <p>
                    Account information collected will be stored with Stishh Media until the user decides to delete their account with Stishh Media or the account has become inactive for a period greater than 1 year. Analytical data is stored with our third-party analytics provider Google for 2-months. After this period, it is replaced with new data collected. We do not share your accounts information with any third-party providers other than our database provider who do not have access to our account on these servers.
